QuestionTxt: Do you favor or oppose the building of a mosque and Islamic community center two blocks from Ground Zero (the site of the September 11, 2001 terrorist attacks on the World Trade Center in New York City)? (If Favor/Oppose, ask:) Do you favor/oppose that strongly, or not that strongly?
StudyNote: The interviews were conducted by land-line and cell phones.  There were parallel surveys conducted of New York City residents and of those who said a close friend or family member was killed on September 11, 2001.
